Files Management:

Flows:
	1. take build to the site directory e.g. /var/www/site_build

Site Configuration

Webserver: apache

dirs: /etc/apache2/
	-> site-available: site.com.conf file
	-> sites-enable: enabled sites
	
	Flow: 
		1. create site.com.conf file
		2. enable the site
		3. restart apache webserver
